      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. can you expand on that? specifically, i want to make sure the essay addresses why the idea of \"meritocracy\"—like the argument that people just get what they deserve through hard work—is basically a myth in this context. how can i frame that so it sounds like a solid critique rather than just an opinion?",
